Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Manufactured Goods
Sub-Industry: Rubber & Plastic
Citadel Plastics Holdings, Inc. operates as a holding company. The Company, through its subsidiaries, manufactures thermoplastic compounds and thermoset resins. Citadel Plastics Holdings markets its products to healthcare, construction, agriculture, automotive, and consumer goods manufacturing industries worldwide.




