Citadel Plastics Holdings was acquired by A. Schulman on March 16, 2015.
                Citadel Plastics Holdings has acquired 4 companies of its own, including 3 in the last 5 years. A total of 3 acquisitions came from private equity firms.
 Citadel Plastics Holdings has acquired in 2 different US states. The Company’s most targeted sectors include building materials (34%) and chemicals (34%).
When analyzing the plastics sector as a whole, according to Mergr, in the last 3 years, there are 49 plastics companies that have made at least 1 acquisition, and 2 have acquired at least 5 companies. The most prolific strategic plastics acquirer over the past 3 years is RPC Group, with 7 acquisitions. The most prolific private equity acquirer in the plastics sector over the past 3 years is Arsenal Capital Partners, Inc. with 2 platform acquisitions.

